17NodeStyle::NodeStyle()
18{
19 // Explicit resources inialization for preventing the static initialization
20 // order fiasco: https://isocpp.org/wiki/faq/ctors#static-init-order
21 initResources();
22 // This configuration is stored inside the compiled unit and is loaded
23 // statically
24 loadJsonFile(":DefaultStyle.json");
25}
26NodeStyle::NodeStyle(QString jsonText)
27{
28 loadJsonText(jsonText);
29}
30void NodeStyle::setNodeStyle(QString jsonText)
31{
32 NodeStyle style(jsonText);
33 StyleCollection::setNodeStyle(style);
34}
35#ifdef STYLE_DEBUG
36 #define NODE_STYLE_CHECK_UNDEFINED_VALUE(v, variable) \
37 { \
38 if (v.type() == QJsonValue::Undefined || v.type() == QJsonValue::Null) \
39 qWarning() << "Undefined value for parameter:" << #variable; \
40 }
41#else
42 #define NODE_STYLE_CHECK_UNDEFINED_VALUE(v, variable)
43#endif
44#define NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(values, variable) \
45 { \
46 auto valueRef = values[#variable]; \
47 NODE_STYLE_CHECK_UNDEFINED_VALUE(valueRef, variable) \
48 if (valueRef.isArray()) \
49 { \
50 auto colorArray = valueRef.toArray(); \
51 std::vector<int> rgb; \
52 rgb.reserve(3); \
53 for (auto it = colorArray.begin(); it != colorArray.end(); ++it) \
54 { \
55 rgb.push_back((*it).toInt()); \
56 } \
57 variable = QColor(rgb[0], rgb[1], rgb[2]); \
58 } \
59 else \
60 { \
61 variable = QColor(valueRef.toString()); \
62 } \
63 }
64#define NODE_STYLE_READ_FLOAT(values, variable) \
65 { \
66 auto valueRef = values[#variable]; \
67 NODE_STYLE_CHECK_UNDEFINED_VALUE(valueRef, variable) \
68 variable = valueRef.toDouble(); \
69 }
70void NodeStyle::loadJsonFile(QString styleFile)
71{
72 QFile file(styleFile);
73 if (!file.open(QIODevice::ReadOnly))
74 {
75 qWarning() << "Couldn't open file " << styleFile;
76 return;
77 }
78 loadJsonFromByteArray(file.readAll());
79}
80void NodeStyle::loadJsonText(QString jsonText)
81{
82 loadJsonFromByteArray(jsonText.toUtf8());
83}
84void NodeStyle::loadJsonFromByteArray(QByteArray const &byteArray)
85{
86 QJsonDocument json(QJsonDocument::fromJson(byteArray));
87 QJsonObject topLevelObject = json.object();
88 QJsonValueRef nodeStyleValues = topLevelObject["NodeStyle"];
89 QJsonObject obj = nodeStyleValues.toObject();
90 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, NormalBoundaryColor);
91 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, SelectedBoundaryColor);
92 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, GradientColor0);
93 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, GradientColor1);
94 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, GradientColor2);
95 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, GradientColor3);
96 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, ShadowColor);
97 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, FontColor);
98 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, FontColorFaded);
99 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, ConnectionPointColor);
100 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, FilledConnectionPointColor);
101 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, WarningColor);
102 NODE_STYLE_READ_COLOR(obj, ErrorColor);
103 NODE_STYLE_READ_FLOAT(obj, PenWidth);
104 NODE_STYLE_READ_FLOAT(obj, HoveredPenWidth);
105 NODE_STYLE_READ_FLOAT(obj, ConnectionPointDiameter);
106 NODE_STYLE_READ_FLOAT(obj, Opacity);
107}
